    "During the training, the learning rate decays, guided by an exponential scheduler with the multiplicative factor set as 0.98.",
    "Kaiming initialization is applied to all neural network parameters.",
    "Hyperparameters are adjustable in the package.",
    "To predict cell state-specific expression, we use the decoder in which the parameters have been learned and optimized by the variational inference.",
    "The proportion c i is adjusted to 1 for a specific cell state and 0 for other cell states."
